@startuml Team Development Workflow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderThickness 2
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888

title Dynamic Travel Architect — Development Cycle\n(Feature / Rule Change Pipeline — Scoped Task Decomposition)

actor "User" as User #LightBlue
participant "Orchestrator\n(Main Context)" as Orch #LightGoldenRodYellow
participant "PM\n(PM-Req)" as PM #LightGreen
participant "Dev\n(Dev-Design / Dev-Impl)" as Dev #LightSkyBlue
participant "SA\n(SA-Review)" as SA #Plum
participant "AE\n(AE-Plan / AE-Impl)" as AE #LightSalmon
participant "QA-A\n(QA-Review)" as QA #Khaki
participant "Render\n(/render skill)" as Render #PeachPuff
participant "Regression\n(/regression skill)" as Regr #MistyRose

== Phase 0: Setup ==

User -> Orch : Feature request / Rule change
activate Orch
Orch -> Orch : Create folder\ntechnical_documents/\nYYYY-MM-DD_change-name/

== Phase 1: Requirements (PM-Req) ==

Orch -> PM : Spawn subagent with\nuser request + relevant rule files
activate PM
PM -> PM : Task 1: Read user request,\nidentify distinct requirements
PM -> PM : Task 2: Write business_requirements.md\n(IDs, descriptions, acceptance criteria)
PM -> PM : Task 3: Identify affected rule files/sections,\nset priority and scope
PM --> Orch : Return summary
deactivate PM
Orch -> Orch : Verify BRD exists on disk

== Phase 2: Design (Dev-Design) ==

Orch -> Dev : Spawn subagent with\nBRD + affected rule files
activate Dev
Dev -> Dev : Task 1: Read BRD + affected rule files
Dev -> Dev : Task 2: Write high_level_design.md\n(components, data flow, dependencies)
Dev -> Dev : Task 3: Write detailed_design.md\n(exact file edits, sections, code changes)
Dev --> Orch : Return summary
deactivate Dev
Orch -> Orch : Verify HLD + DD exist on disk

== Phase 3: Architecture Review (SA-Review) ==

Orch -> SA : Spawn subagent with\nBRD + HLD + DD + architecture rules
activate SA
SA -> SA : Task 1: Review for content/presentation separation
SA -> SA : Task 2: Review for extensibility
SA -> SA : Task 3: Review for pattern consistency
SA -> SA : Task 4: Write architecture_review.md\n(Approved / Approved with changes / Rejected)

alt #FFE0E0 SA Rejects (max 2 retries)
    SA --> Orch : Rejected + feedback
    deactivate SA

    loop retry ≤ 2
        Orch -> Dev : Re-spawn Dev-Design with DD +\narchitecture_review.md feedback
        activate Dev
        Dev -> Dev : Task 4: Address SA feedback,\nrevise HLD + DD
        Dev --> Orch : Updated design
        deactivate Dev

        Orch -> SA : Re-spawn SA review
        activate SA
        SA -> SA : Re-review revised design
        alt SA Approves
            SA --> Orch : Approved
            deactivate SA
        else SA Still Rejects
            SA --> Orch : Rejected again
            deactivate SA
        end
    end

    note over Orch : If still rejected after\n2 retries → escalate to User
else #E0FFE0 SA Approves
    SA --> Orch : Approved
    deactivate SA
end

== Phase 4a: Test Planning (AE-Plan) ==

Orch -> AE : Spawn subagent with\nBRD + DD + automation rules
activate AE
AE -> AE : Task 1: Map each BRD acceptance\ncriterion to test cases
AE -> AE : Task 2: Write test_plan.md
AE --> Orch : Return summary
deactivate AE
Orch -> Orch : Verify test_plan.md exists

== Phase 4b: QA Architecture Review (QA-Review) ==

Orch -> QA : Spawn subagent with\nBRD + test_plan + automation rules
activate QA
QA -> QA : Task 1: Review for BRD coverage completeness
QA -> QA : Task 2: Review for duplicate tests
QA -> QA : Task 3: Review correct fixtures, assertions, POM
QA -> QA : Task 4: Write qa_architecture_review.md\n(Approved / Rejected + feedback)

alt #FFE0E0 QA-A Rejects (max 2 retries)
    QA --> Orch : Rejected + feedback
    deactivate QA

    loop retry ≤ 2
        Orch -> AE : Re-spawn AE-Plan with test_plan +\nqa_architecture_review.md feedback
        activate AE
        AE -> AE : Task 3: Address QA-A feedback,\nrevise test_plan.md
        AE --> Orch : Updated plan
        deactivate AE

        Orch -> QA : Re-spawn QA-A review
        activate QA
        QA -> QA : Re-review revised plan
        alt QA-A Approves
            QA --> Orch : Approved
            deactivate QA
        else QA-A Still Rejects
            QA --> Orch : Rejected again
            deactivate QA
        end
    end

    note over Orch : If still rejected after\n2 retries → escalate to User
else #E0FFE0 QA-A Approves
    QA --> Orch : Approved
    deactivate QA
end

== Phase 5: Implementation (Dev-Impl + AE-Impl in Parallel) ==

note over Dev, AE #LightYellow
    Dev-Impl and AE-Impl run in parallel.
    **File ownership enforced:**
    Dev-Impl → rule files, content, rendering code
    AE-Impl → test specs, TripPage.ts, release_notes.md
end note

Orch -> Dev : Spawn Dev-Impl subagent with\nDD + relevant source files
activate Dev
Orch -> AE : Spawn AE-Impl subagent with\ntest_plan + TripPage.ts + automation rules
activate AE

Dev -> Dev : Task 1: Implement code changes\nper approved DD
AE -> AE : Tasks 1-6: Implement tests\nper approved test_plan
AE -> AE : Task 7: Update release_notes.md

Dev --> Orch : Code changes complete
deactivate Dev
AE --> Orch : Test implementation complete
deactivate AE

== Phase 6: Validation (AE-Exec) ==

Orch -> Render : Spawn as subagent\n(generate HTML fragments → assemble)
activate Render
Render -> Render : Per-day fragment generation
Render -> Render : Assemble into\ntrip_full_LANG.html
Render -> Render : Pre-regression validation
Render --> Orch : HTML generation complete
deactivate Render

Orch -> Regr : Spawn as subagent\n(run full regression suite)
activate Regr
Regr -> Regr : AE-Exec Task 1: Run progression tests\n(new/changed features)
Regr -> Regr : AE-Exec Task 2: Run full regression suite
Regr -> Regr : AE-Exec Task 3: Generate Playwright HTML report\n(with traces & screenshots)
Regr --> Orch : Test results + report
deactivate Regr

== PM Acceptance (PM-Accept) ==

Orch -> Orch : Report BRD acceptance\ncriteria coverage based\non regression results

alt #FFE0E0 Tests Fail
    Orch -> Orch : Loop back to Phase 5\n(fix code or tests)
else #E0FFE0 All Tests Pass
    Orch --> User : Delivery complete\n(BRD criteria met ✓)
    deactivate Orch
end

@enduml
